    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\overline {a}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/032e261791bd07a59cf1419352fc66f7901d4b1a" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.345ex; height:2.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\overline {a}}}"></span> denote the congruence class containing the integer <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">a</span>,<sup id="cite&#95;ref-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-6"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>6<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup> then
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\overline {a}}=\{b\in \mathbb {Z} \mid a\equiv b{\pmod {m}}\}.}">
  <semantics>
