</p><p>In the case that <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">m</span> is a <a href="/wiki/Prime_number" title="Prime number">prime</a>, say <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">p</span>, then <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \phi (p)=p-1}">
