<p>In the special case where <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">m</span> is a prime, <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \phi (m)=m-1}">
